### Backend API Test Dosyası
### VS Code REST Client extension ile kullanılabilir

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123456",
  "display_name": "Test User"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123456"
}

### Get All Habits (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Habit (requires auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Su içmek",
  "description": "Günde 8 bardak su içmek",
  "recurrence": "daily",
  "difficulty": 1,
  "color": "#4A90E2",
  "reminder_time": "09:00"
}

### Check Habit (requires auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits/{{habitId}}/check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "completed": true
}

### Get Character (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Character (requires auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/characters
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "dog",
  "custom_name": "Max"
}

### Get Achievements (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/achievements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

